Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.19,OP English,,0,0,0,,I'll still be laughing in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:10.05,OP English,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's a sailor uniform. ←Q.E.D.!
