Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that even the most generous people...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...complain about a single yen difference when it comes to gasoline?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that book I loaned to you a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they're making a game out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously I'm not gonna buy it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so behind, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I pre-ordered the limited edition the moment the news broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I also bought the DVD box set for the anime and other related goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're into it more than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty common for someone to become more addicted than the person who recommended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how Yui-neesan bought her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to someone else's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Her car!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I lent her a racing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It surprised even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary how much energy people can put into their hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday makes it three victories in a row, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's the start of a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If we keep winning like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the playoffs and Japan Series aren't out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.35,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.61,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I believe it's pro baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:37.36,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Sensei likes that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, baseball is all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.84,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh, speaking of baseball,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The famous poet, Masaoka Shiki, loved baseball so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He played as a catcher until the day he could no longer play due to his illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He changed his name to Noboru,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrote it using the characters for baseball, calling himself Noball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the winners of the Major League are called the world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about the Japan Series reminded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's only American teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They should beat our team first before they call themselves world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's quite pumped up, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It smelled pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you show me how to do these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How rare,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you asking a question about schoolwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some pretty difficult questions in here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's because they're the questions from a quiz game at the arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good with academics, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you put more effort into studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a college applicant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I might seem like that here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but over there I'm considered a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you just enroll in that academy of yours already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I'm a little sleep deprived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How long were you up doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, you always go to sleep around 11, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Though looking at Miyuki-san reminded me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the fact that you sleep a lot, you haven't grown all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Onee-chan told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm so conscientious about the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for calling so late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the Iwasaki residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, may I speak with Minami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to bed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she usually go to sleep this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pittan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,La La moji-pittan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be having fun singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll let my father know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right after the ground-blessing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, that's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, there you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still underage, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't see the gestures on the other side of the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm on the phone, I need to focus on the conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have to put the controller down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But then your hands just feel so empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the other day, I took a roller and started cleaning up my floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just rolling away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like that can actually get pretty addicting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like random doodles or menial chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,once you get off the phone, you don't want to do those tasks anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's depressing when you see that just the area around you is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My passion disappears when the call ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just leave it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's pretty smelly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's okay once in a while, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,**cky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Poc**!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I remember doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of things we did as kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,do you remember stirring your yogurt and going, "Bread Factory!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy and try explaining it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the game I lent to you back during the first semester?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else wants to play it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so do you think I could have it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it for the squirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, I've lent quite a few to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I should get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure are amazing, Hiiragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I found some games the other day and I had no idea who they belonged to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you can remember something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are a few I've loaned to other people that I've forgotten about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How careless can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be a Law of Equivalent Lending, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a universal truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hiiragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what's u{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Potemkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it was something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's important, don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at the numbers for the Autumn Jumbo Lottery,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't win any.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it isn't so easy to win these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I submitted a lot of postcards, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't win any prizes from the drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When you lose so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you start to wonder if...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...the vendors or the editors are doing something fishy, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be so suspicious of people like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go to sleep for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, I need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They say I talk too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sleepy earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so why am I wide awake after saying such a stupid joke like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just no good at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I should just go to sleep while I'm dozing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really sleepy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so why did I become wide awake when I got under the cold sheets?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm tonight, so maybe I can fall asleep right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason my feet are really warm, so I can't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I the only person like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly the season for yakimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, so please don't remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll make me fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you said it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once my eyes met with the old man's, {I have a lot of patience for derp sentences, but this is too derp. Alt.: "I had already made eye contact with the storekeeper/old man, so it would've been rude if I didn't buy it." The "Y'NO?" is redundant because of line 230.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd have been rude not to buy one, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, is she going to buy one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Or is she just going to walk the other way?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I totally know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When your eyes meet at Comiket, it's hard to put the book back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep on talking even when people have no idea what you're talking about, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about when you're standing in front of a circle's booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When you pick up a book in front of an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel bad leaving without buying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But you put it down anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been a lot of light novels adapted into anime series recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The novel I loaned you a while back,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,has already had three anime adaptations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And there should be a new volume coming out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched the anime, but I haven't read the novels yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many words, so I just get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The games you always play have a lot more text than a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you would think, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd really help if they released them in a visual novel format.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,when is the fourth season coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to be some kind of reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-chan, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The lid keeps going on crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, some people are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they're just clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's those cute little flaws that make you similar to Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You are amazing after all, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I closed it like I normally would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't open the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should just tear it open along the notches?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll open it properly, so just wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just tear it open along the notches or use scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, my pride won't let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll leave me feeling like I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, is it a mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get frustrated just knowing that there's one in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you haven't been bitten yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you know they're there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you must take them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my hunters instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If a guy in our class confesses his love for me or Yu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,does it make that guy a lolicon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're in the same class year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so technically it wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But in this case, there would be an emphasis on your appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypothetically,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were a 30-year-old who looked like a grade schooler,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,then you could say that guy is into older women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite a complicated issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to come up with a strict interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're definitely my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were Kagami, she would just say, "Does it matter!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And end the conversation right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fell in love with Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and dote on a daughter like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't it make you a lolicon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're a bit mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I like normal girls, too, not just little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you should say I'm also a lolicon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I suppose it depends on the character we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, you fail as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how you're so attached to me and follow me everywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you still be like that if I was a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad I'm a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the bath is almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go ahead, Yu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you had to chase her away to keep your image.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She was really short,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and was your childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she seem like a character out of a gal-game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata was always adorable since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why you fell for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but why did she marry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like, "Because you wouldn't look at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I became this gal-game loving man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she just accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that coercion!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of course that wasn't the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you were born, Konata, she was really happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"I wonder if she got this mole from you, Sou-kun?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well, she certainly has your eyes, Kanata."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"No matter how you look at her, you can definitely tell she's our child."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want her to grow up taking the good traits from both of us."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"I hope she doesn't inherit my height...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...or your personality."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"That was pretty harsh."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you ask about Kanata all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really know much about Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lonely without Mom around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You create enough excitement for two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have Yu-chan here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata's grown up to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Though maybe not quite as normal as you would have wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't die before me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I have no intention to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata passed away young,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but until the very end, she smiled and said she was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's pretty hard for those left behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can be happy like that at the end, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe from a moé overdose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you're not gonna have a proper death are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought a digital camera for work today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've visited this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.80,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.01,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,C'mon, just one more picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what those two are doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:02.90,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.50,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I was in the middle of a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.33,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.34,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay, say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dad, you're way too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being really cold, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to take some pictures to commemorate my new camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it supposed to be for work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, don't be so stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.58,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,One more picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.42,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,That's right, you never did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.78,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,...pay much attention to other people's circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You really haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel more and more like Kanata when I hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just blurt out such dangerous comments!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see what Mom had to put up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad may be like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't just turn to bad behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When you clear that game,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,teach me how to play it, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's actually pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.48,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I think I made a wrong selection,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they play games together as a family,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.87,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Somewhere along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess they're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:13.59,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm having a hard time getting to the H-scene with the character I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you letting our daughter play?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you teaching her the wrong thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Mom choose you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're just an old perverted, lolicon, otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would go for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bit harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure don't go easy on your old man, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how I should put this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:39.88,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata had a pretty good intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.96,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,you were always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.45,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I almost forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.28,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Why I chose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I failed as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:53.08,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,To spend the rest of my life with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one thing I was absolutely sure about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing that you were absolutely sure about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...loved Kanata more than anyone else in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was no match after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He accepted my good traits and my bad ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was willing to show me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...his good traits as well as his bad ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The place where I can feel most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The place that could make me feel the most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough reminiscing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take more with Yu-chan later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:25.24,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,The fact that I can no longer be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said only one more last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.84,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,is a little painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought this for your own hobby, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just testing it out before I start using it for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.24,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how the two of them exist within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can live on inside of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll continue to watch over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.44,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,May the ones who brought me so much joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...be blessed with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.38,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll be surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This picture...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a person's shadow in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A real ghost picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath's ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-Yu-Yu-Yu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or we'll be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, don't erase it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Erasing it may not be enough, don't we have to burn it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't erase it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've talked with her a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a different impression of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still think Mina-rin is a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:50.62,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Those two sure are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in charge of the classroom chores today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Sensei still in the faculty office?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:52.22,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,This would be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yutaka, your tie is crooked."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"O-Onee-sama!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't look at my friends like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's been building up inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you can't find them anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't find their manager either?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They were gonna get fired, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The camera's rolling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling about this show from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually refused in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was all that politics crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Grown-up issues and whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that the camera is rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nakajima?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it's the medley version!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-Miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For-For-For-Forgot my something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One clear, sunshiny day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it! For I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa Mo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-Miracle Minorun-run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For-For-For-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One clear, sunshiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it! For...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikaider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa Moni...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For-For-For-Forgot my something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing I left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One clear, sunshiny day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it! For I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.05,0:22:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Shikaider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa Moni...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Shikaider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa Moni...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For I am Shikaider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For-For-For-For-For-For!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Minorun-run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For I am Shikaider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't change when I blew the whistle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept ending on Shikaider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And next week on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Soujirou here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Sou-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be heading off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to separate my spirit from my body yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure I can learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun, you're talking about manga or anime again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "A Fine Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fly with all the turbulence!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
